# Logic Flows

- `docs/logic_flows` is the durable source for scholar-authored reasoning, dawah methodology and AI response guidance.
- Keep religious reasoning, tone guidance and reusable prompt context in Markdown here instead of hardcoding it into UI components.
- Preserve original meaning and cite supporting references when content introduces claims.
- Structure files so agents can retrieve context predictably: premises, progression, common objections, supporting references and tone guidance.
- Avoid mixing temporary product copy with long-lived methodology.
- When app prompts depend on this content, keep the dependency clear in code comments or naming.
